data.description: Charming mid-century expansion thoughtfully finished throughout. Oak hardwood floors, bright spaces, two main floor bedrooms and large upper owner's bedroom with large closet, storage and half bath. Sunny eat-in kitchen with plenty of storage and space. Beautifully finished lower level offers family room, entertaining area with snack area & beverage frig, large bedroom with egress window. Laundry area with additional storage. Updated mechanicals including roof, main floor windows, and Carrier furnace & central air. Large, fenced yard with deck. Garage with opener. A welcoming home in quiet Shingle Creek neighborhood just blocks from walking paths and ponds. A beautiful opportunity!
